BusinessTech has had an excellent start to 2022, with a record number of advertising campaigns booked on the site. As South Africa’s largest business news website, BusinessTech is the go-to online platform for the country’s key business decision makers. This makes it the perfect place for companies who want to reach an influential business audience to advertise on. Sponsored articles with social media amplification, display banners, homepage takeovers, and Business Talk sponsorships have proven particularly popular in the past month. BusinessTech has also had an exceptionally strong start to 2022 in terms of its audience numbers. Over 5 million South African readers have visited BusinessTech this month, placing it far ahead of other business news websites. The majority of these readers are C-level executives, business owners, company directors, managers, and professionals. These readers are highly influential in terms of the purchasing decisions their businesses make, thanks to their positions of authority. BusinessTech offers a range of advertising options which makes it easy to reach its influential audience. Companies only have to say which audience they want to reach, and BusinessTech takes care of the rest. Click here to find out more about advertising on BusinessTech.